column5: Have a question for you. Need some help.  Thanks
Not directly in HVAC, but it's sister refrigeration. PM sent.
I do mostly commercial HVAC, Not up to date on current residential makes a models but can find out from suppliers, you can PM me with any questions if you wish
I'm a licensed sheet metal worker... If it's metal related pm me

I also need a bit of work done on my basement heater which was originally designed for an RV home. Had a small leak that reliance found and they turned the system off for me. Please PM if interested in some side $.
Thanks for all the help guys! My builder is looking in to it
Did you get my reply to your PM ?
I've used Stanton Mechanical out of Kitchener for both residential and commercial. Great work, great service if you need something.
